STATE of North Carolina
v.
Marshall AUSTIN. No. 119P08. Supreme Court of North Carolina. April 10, 2008. Marshall Leon Austin, Pro Se. LaToya B. Powell, Assistant Attorney General, R. Stuart Albright, District Attorney, for State of NC.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 10th day of March 2008 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the Superior Court, Guilford County, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court of that County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 10th day of April 2008."
